2	//!
3	//! Each primitive's output is asserted against known-good numeric
4	//! results. The numbers here match what `mlpl_runtime::call_builtin`
5	//! produces for the same input (hand-verified against step-005's
6	//! existing eval tests); keeping the check numeric here avoids a
